methods.findKeys:
Find keys and deliver them to the locationKeyObserver.

:param locationKeyObserver: (java.util.function.Consumer<KeyValuePartitionLayout.TLK>) - Per-key callback

text:
Location finder that will traverse a directory hierarchy and infer partitions from
 key-value pairs in the directory names, for example:
 tableRootDirectory/Country=France/City=Paris/parisData.parquet
 Traversal is depth-first, and assumes that target files will only be found at a single depth.
